{"tid":2167310,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【35+植物人召喚】政府刊憲今年10月14日為新一個立法年度開始日期","createTime":"2020-08-21T04:40:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T15:49:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"86cea24df80885a665cdbb5ce6632e86c010873e","tid":2167310,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T04:40:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545052-20200821.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545052-20200821.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu6C2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=285db5bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1545052-20200821.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d0c5f7d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1545052-20200821.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n政府刊憲，行政長官林鄭月娥根據《立法會條例》，指明今年10月14日為新一個立法年度開始的日期。<br />\n<br />\n政府早前決定，因應疫情推遲立法會換屆選舉一年，全國人大常委會其後作出決定，現屆立法會議員繼續履行職責不少於一年。"},{"pid":"b3234cfa9aba23ed41bdc9bdb9e01af07bcf41de","tid":2167310,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T15:49:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}